<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zài nà yáo yuǎn de shān jiǎo xià 迦南1094</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài nà yáo yuǎn de shān jiǎo xià, zhù zhe yī hù hù rén jiā.
 cóng méi tīng jiàn guò fú yīn, wǒ men yào xiàng nà de chū fā.
 gēn suí shèng líng de yǐn dǎo, zǒu guò chūn qiū dōng xià.
 xún zhǎo wèi dé zhī mín, yīn yé sū kuài huí lái le.
 chū fā ya chū fā, chū fā ya chū fā.
 shén zhèng zài xíng xīn shì, zài nà yáo yuǎn de shān jiǎo xià.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1094</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>